			</distracter>
			<distracter oae-label="#5">
				<![CDATA[]]>
			</distracter>
			<distracter oae-label="#6">
				<![CDATA[]]>
			</distracter>
		</distracters>
	</page>
	<page>
				<audio oae-label="audio file name (optional). Please include the file extension (.mp3)" oae-type="textarea" oae-rows="1">
		<![CDATA[]]>
	</audio>
	<text oae-label="Text" oae-type="textarea" oae-rows="25">
			<![CDATA[<b>A:</b>     Tell me about your parents.
<b>B:</b>     &nbsp;<blank word="My father is an artist." align="left"/>
<b>A:</b>     Really?  How old is he?
<b>B:</b>     &nbsp;<blank word="Forty-two." align="left"/>
<b>A:</b>     He's so young.  How about your mother?  How old is she?
<b>B:</b>     &nbsp;<blank word="She’s thirty-six." align="left"/>
<b>A:</b>     My mother is thirty-six, too.  What does your mother do?
<b>B:</b>     &nbsp;<blank word="She’s a chef." align="left"/>]]>
		</text>

